    "spell": {
        "name": "Grasping Vine",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "A thick, curling vine erupts from the ground beneath you and stretches to the target, allowing you to move it around. If the target is an item, you can move it 10 feet in any direction within range when you Cast the Spell and the first time you Sustain it each round. If the target is a creature, they must attempt a Reflex save.",
